path.id: *Hover on a rectangle to view its thumbnails
The context in which people are represented in thumbnails.
The colors of the boxes indicates the gender of person represented in thumbnails.
The size of the boxes and thumbnails indicates the number of views of the videos.
*Thumbnails in this category are selected on the basis of the object being more important than the person, whose body is clearly presented and serve as a background to the object.
**Thumbnails in this category have persons presented in a situation that suggests sexual connotations, but does not directly relate to sexuality.
